name: Rocket Boost (Cheese Studios)
description:
IMPORTANT: Click the blue full-screen button to avoid cut-off.

Rocket Boost is an exciting game where you control a test rocket in a rocket testing facility. You must test to see if the rocket will be able to make it to the end of the level without hitting any of the obstacles on the way.  After you complete the ten levels the rocket will complete its training.

Controls: A - Rotate left   D - Rotate right   Space Bar - Boost (Go forward in the direction your facing)

Game made by Cheese Studios

Cheese Studio's Website: https://sites.google.com/view/cheese-studios/home?authuser=0
